{"tid":1595201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[926] 灣仔六校料築人鏈圍高官","createTime":"2019-09-26T02:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T04:05:22.000Z","uid":56881,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1fef5fe8e2c0d644c583effc6ee5aea0a079a1c2","tid":1595201,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:38:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%85%AD%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%99%E7%AF%89%E4%BA%BA%E9%8F%88%E5%9C%8D%E9%AB%98%E5%AE%98-214500795.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%2596%2599%25E7%25AF%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%258F%2588%25E5%259C%258D%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25AE%2598-214500795.html&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=01f7e2de\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%85%AD%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%99%E7%AF%89%E4%BA%BA%E9%8F%88%E5%9C%8D%E9%AB%98%E5%AE%98-214500795.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8u2lVuM.pE1qz7ctvequYQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/d26a0d0f6eea67606e60352b6c3081b4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F8u2lVuM.pE1qz7ctvequYQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fd26a0d0f6eea67606e60352b6c3081b4&h=bd30ad7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n灣仔多間學校決定今天提早放學。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】首場「社區對話」殺到，部分學校及家長憂慮屆時有大型示威或堵路，擔心學生安全，灣仔及銅鑼灣附近一帶至少十間學校決定提早放學。而灣仔區六間學校的學生及校友亦發起在下午築起人鏈，「迎接」出席對話的官員，冀當局了解學生訴求。<br />\n<br />\n安全考慮 部分學校提早下課<br />\n<br />\n受影響學校更改學生活動日程，令學生可提早離開學校。教育局發言人指，一直與學校保持聯絡了解學校情況，部分灣仔區學校基於學生安全考慮，今提早下課。局方已提醒學校必須事先通知家長及其他持份者有關詳情，並須提醒學生放學後要盡快回家，切勿參與可能出現混亂和危險的活動，遠離危險的地方。<br />\n<br />\n六間學校的學生及校友發起今午四時半在伊館附近築人鏈，響應的包括香港鄧鏡波書院、嘉諾撒聖方濟各書院、香港華仁書院、聖公會鄧肇堅中學、鄧肇堅維多利亞官立中學及香港真光中學，學生擬於活動開始前，以和平、理性及非暴力形式促請港府正面回應市民訴求，並要求當局承認警隊肆意襲擊市民及為此道歉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑暗中的對話"},{"pid":"8997bf9702cb1eb698edd7cad84c2480074c4e56","tid":1595201,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:40:12.000Z","msg":"［香港獨立！唯一辦法！］<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z6MVGwi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ6MVGwi.jpg&h=1ed93f00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JWKL3KV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJWKL3KV.jpg&h=63206eed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4dGKzOZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4dGKzOZ.jpg&h=bcba39e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aqWCakp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaqWCakp.jpg&h=6804524c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hbFLjcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhbFLjcd.jpg&h=70135473&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【警世】不要再執迷於追求五大訴求<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1594691\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1594691</a>"},{"pid":"628d03d568dd72ab8865be29fd8bfca8907a1240","tid":1595201,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:42:18.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"322c8b74fdf04acbe96e6e7c02450c5671efca69","tid":1595201,"uid":91230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:46:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e1adf14183d2ffda50304691e802d7ff905d9da","tid":1595201,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:46:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261c383831063857ae3c23e7cd88d860e25fda21","tid":1595201,"uid":91230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T03:44:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span